lead_paragraph: The Los Angeles Kings can't win in regulation, and they're unbeatable in extra time. They fail to score a goal for a full week, and then they outscore the defending Stanley Cup champions.

headline.print_headline: Nic Dowd's OT Goal Gives Kings 3-2 Win Over Penguins
headline.main: Nic Dowd's OT Goal Gives Kings 3-2 Win Over Penguins
